name: 杰克·史密斯
introduction: Jake Smith, best known for his work in #Roxy (2018) is a Canadian actor, born in Stratford, Ontario. He found his interest in acting and film during high school and soon after graduating, moved to Toronto to attend film school. While in college for film production, his love of acting only grew stronger while taking part in multiple short films as well as starting to focus on his training at Armstrong Acting studio.After studying and refining his skills in acting, Jake soon signed on with Bryan Misener at The Characters Talent Agency, quickly leading to landing his first large professional roll as Lee in #Roxy (2018)
